# RecMode .gitignore — .NET / WPF / portable app

## Build output
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
publish/
artifacts/
/dist/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Rider / VS / VS Code
.idea/
.vs/
*.vsidx
# keep .vscode workspace files that are checked in intentionally

## Test / coverage
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
coverage/
*.coverage
*.trx

## NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.packages/
packages/

## RecMode runtime state (portable mode writes here — never commit)
/Data/
/Recordings/
src/**/Data/
**/portable-out/

## Bundled ffmpeg binaries (large; acquired by tooling, not committed)
/ffmpeg/*.exe
/ffmpeg/*.dll
tools/ffmpeg/*.exe
tools/ffmpeg/*.dll

## Logs / dumps / temp
*.log
*.dmp
*.tmp
crash/

## OS cruft
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
